 	<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><a href="https://news.utm.my/2025/03/qs-wur-by-subject-2025-petroleum-engineering-breaks-into-the-global-top-50-data-science-ai-debuts-in-the-top-100/"><b>Top Subject Rankings</b></a><b>:</b> <span style="font-weight: 400;">UTM continues to shine in the QS World University Rankings by Subject 2025. </span><b>Petroleum Engineering</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> remains in the </span><b>top 50 worldwide, while  Architecture</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> is  ranked </span><b>#1 in Malaysia</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> and placed among the </span><b>top 100 globally</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">. Our  </span><b>first-ever entry for Artificial Intelligence and Data Science</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> earned a spot in the </span><b>top 100</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">, marking a significant milestone for the university.</span></li>
