 	<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><a href="https://news.utm.my/2024/11/utm-ranked-1-in-malaysia-by-the-interdisciplinary-science-rankings-2025/"><b>THE Interdisciplinary Science Rankings 2025</b></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">: UTM proudly secured the </span><b>#1 spot in Malaysia</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> and </span><b>35th globally</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">, showcasing our leadership in solving complex global challenges through interdisciplinary research.</span></li>
